T02TD3751E:85b-1: au tsushma dzambha la au pa de sha sto tra /
T02TD3751E:85b-3: rmugs 'dzin 'chol ba'i man ngag gi bstod pa /
T02TD3751E:85b-4: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3751E:85b-5: mgon po nam mkha'i mdog can nor gyi char 'bebs pa //
T02TD3751E:85b-6: ma skyes rang bzhin dag pas sku mdog nag por bzhugs //
T02TD3751E:85b-7: khyod ni rdo rje sems dpa' nyid de bdag dran na //
T02TD3751E:85b-8: khyod la 'dud kyis thugs rjes ci yi phyir mi gzigs //
T02TD3751E:85b-9: lo drug byis pa'i gzugs la gzhon pa'i sha rgyas pa //
T02TD3751E:85b-10: 'dzum la khro la byams pa'i mche ba dkar po gtsigs //
T02TD3751E:85b-11: khro gnyer dpral bar bsnyer zhing ral pa dmar ser langs //
T02TD3751E:85b-12: dbul ba sel mdzad spyan yangs snying rje can la 'dud //
T02TD3751E:85b-13: mi bskyod dbu la bzhugs bas thugs kyi rig 'dzin cing //
T02TD3751E:85b-14: byams pas kun la khros te gcir bu sprul gyis brgyan //
T02TD3751E:85b-15: aom aa las skyes nor sbyin gdan la bzhugs shing 'gying //
T02TD3751E:85b-16: re ba skong mdzad dpag bsam shing 'dra khyod la 'dud //
T02TD3751E:85b-17: phyag g-yas snying rjes don mdzad thod pa khrag gis bkang //
T02TD3751E:85b-18: phyag g-yon nor spyin ma bzung ne'u les rin chen 'bebs //
T02TD3751E:85b-19: g-yas g-yon zhabs kyis rnam thos sras kyi rkang brdzis //
T02TD3751E:85b-20: nor bdag gan rkyal gnon cing brgyad bskum bzhugs la 'dud //
T02TD3751E:85b-21: rnam ba ma phug rigs ngan cha lugs lhag ma za //
T02TD3751E:85b-22: lag nas kha ru 'o ma'i bdud rtsi rtsa lam rdo rje nas byung ste //
T02TD3751E:86a-1: mdog 'dra zhal du phul bas mnyes mdzod la //
T02TD3751E:86a-2: nyid kyis bdag gi bsam mkhyen re ba myur du skongs //
T02TD3751E:86a-3: yi ge bcu pas byin brlabs me tog dang bcas pas //
T02TD3751E:86a-4: aom las 'od 'phros gdub bu rin chen spras pas brgyan //
T02TD3751E:86a-5: aom las byung ba'i bum pa bzang pos chu phul nas //
T02TD3751E:86a-6: bcom ldan mgon po ci phyir re ba mi bskong lags //
T02TD3751E:86a-7: 'gro drug kun la re bskong nor gyi char pa dag / ci 'dod mang po 'bebs pa'i thugs rje grags lags na //
T02TD3751E:86a-8: bdag gis mos pas khyod kyi yon tan rtag tu brjod //
T02TD3751E:86a-9: thigs pa gcig kyang mi stsol skal pa med dam ci ;
T02TD3751E:86a-10: / nyi ma re re bzhin du rtag tu khyod 'bod na //
T02TD3751E:86a-11: bdag ni yi chad sgyid lugs gdong pa dag mod kyang //
T02TD3751E:86a-12: khyod kyi sngon gyi dam bcas thugs rje gang du thal //
T02TD3751E:86a-13: gter chen skal ba med kyang log 'tsho med tsam byin //
T02TD3751E:86a-14: bdag gis snying nas smras kyang da dung ma gzigs na //
T02TD3751E:86a-15: sa gsum kun la snyoms par dam ni ma bcas sam //
T02TD3751E:86a-16: bdag la skal ba med kyang thugs rjes cis mi gzigs //
T02TD3751E:86a-17: sems can min nam dbul pa'i sdug bsngal bral par mdzod //
T02TD3751E:86a-18: bdag gis bos pas khyod kyi thugs rje'i zhags pa yis //
T02TD3751E:86a-19: srid 'dir dbul ba sol ba bde chen gnas su drongs ;
T02TD3751E:86a-20: /'jigs la 'jigs par mi byed khyod kyis byin brlabs te //
T02TD3751E:86a-21: 'di dang pha rol gnyis kar rtag tu bskyab par mdzod //
T02TD3751E:86a-22: rmugs 'dzin 'chol ba'i man ngag gi bstod pa bla ma dha byang chub sems dpas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD3751E:86a-24: // / kha cig slob dpon nyi ma sbas pas mdzad do zhes kyang zer skad do//
